@BookingManagement_Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7022
@resourceId = meeting-room-a
@userId = user-001

### 1) Get seeded resources
GET {{BookingManagement_Api_HostAddress}}/api/resources
Accept: application/json

###

### 2) Get seeded users
GET {{BookingManagement_Api_HostAddress}}/api/users
Accept: application/json

###

### 3) Create a booking
POST {{BookingManagement_Api_HostAddress}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "resourceId": "{{resourceId}}",
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "startDateTime": "2026-07-03T09:00:00Z",
  "endDateTime": "2026-07-03T10:00:00Z"
}

###

### 4) Get bookings for one resource
GET {{BookingManagement_Api_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/resource/{{resourceId}}?fromUtc=2026-07-01T00:00:00Z&toUtc=2026-07-31T23:59:59Z&includeCancelled=true&pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

###

### 5) Try overlapping booking - expected result: 409 Conflict
POST {{BookingManagement_Api_HostAddress}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "resourceId": "{{resourceId}}",
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "startDateTime": "2026-07-03T09:30:00Z",
  "endDateTime": "2026-07-03T10:30:00Z"
}

###

### 6) Cancel a booking
# Copy the id returned from request 3 and replace it below.
POST {{BookingManagement_Api_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/E1742EB8-756B-4D05-9B03-BE57A0B1EB8A/cancel
Accept: application/json